Body: Description: EPP started to block WinSCP for exempted domains. Tried to collect diagnostic data from the device but it is not working, and there is no informative log from this activity that could allow us to troubleshoot that.
What We've Learned Updated: Customer use a script to file transfer multiple files at the time. The file transfers are made through their network share, that are added in allow list.
Next Steps Updated: Update the ADO ticket with the newest details.
Next Steps Updated: We agree with the customer to wait until. the offline patch for 5.9.4.1 version, so we can try with it and check if is still reproducible .
